snippet: Jan 3, 2023 ... ... a hospital bed above water while themselves being submerged was produced in 2020 by an Iranian artist named Bozorgmehr Hossainpour.
htmlSnippet: Jan 3, 2023 ... ... a hospital bed above water while themselves being submerged was produced in 2020 by an Iranian artist named Bozorgmehr Hossainpour.

metatags.twitter:creator: @Reuters
metatags.og:description: A cartoon showing a healthcare worker holding a hospital bed above water while themselves being submerged was produced in 2020 by an Iranian artist named Bozorgmehr Hossainpour. It is not a piece drawn by graffiti artist Banksy, as has been claimed online.
